- cs.SD (Sound) is also a likely category as the paper focuses on acoustic models and their use in speech recognition.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category as the paper proposes a new architecture for deep learning models.
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is a possible category as the paper presents results on a large scale video dataset.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper proposes a new approach to deep learning models that could have broader applications beyond speech recognition.
